OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774537862
OL,3,CTransport boss 'horrified' as ITV
OL,4,CLondon uncovers shocking bus driver
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,F"There is recognition at senior levels
OL,8,Fthat this needs to improve and what we
OL,9,Fneed to do is make sure, as with any
OL,10,Flarge organisation, be it TfL, a bus
OL,11,Foperator, a railway company or an
OL,12,Fairline, is making sure that the
OL,13,Fpeople, leaders and line managers
OL,14,Facross the organisation act
OL,15,Fappropriately and respond
OL,16,Fappropriately in the event of
OL,17,Fcolleagues needing support for
OL,18,Fwhatever reason.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
